snippet.textDisplay: Truly a special theme this, one of the greats. This theme means alot to me, even as a kid i could tell it was something special. From the awesome build up at the beginning that just gets behind you, it drives you into the awesome adventure that was the world. It's richer than anything around at the time (and still now), that touch of melancholy but excitement, man what a song. To me the build up at the start and the whole thing says 'you know what?, screw it, let's get to the awesome part and stay there because it's awesome'. There's a feeling of freedom in the song. Anyway just thought i'd comment on prob the most iconic super turrican song :)
